    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MENTAL SAGA</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A  game with a strong narrative component that incorporates several styles of action-oriented gameplay. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two parallel stories, one told through the gameplay itself and another told through an interactable comic book that serves as an interlude between levels.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE MISTERY</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265020/extras/297b5f1813a363d2a2de92d61b0f4d0f.poster.avif?t=1769452305\" width=426 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265020/extras/297b5f1813a363d2a2de92d61b0f4d0f.webm?t=1769452305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265020/extras/297b5f1813a363d2a2de92d61b0f4d0f.mp4?t=1769452305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are trapped in a ... backpack!? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This backpack seems to act like a dimensional portal, but what really is it?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DIFFERENT GAMEPLAY STYLES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265020/extras/2cd83d708a42f131362970b8afcea7e0.poster.avif?t=1769452305\" width=426 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265020/extras/2cd83d708a42f131362970b8afcea7e0.webm?t=1769452305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265020/extras/2cd83d708a42f131362970b8afcea7e0.mp4?t=1769452305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265020/extras/604cb32a73cb9db20715382b6d6b9be8.poster.avif?t=1769452305\" width=426 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265020/extras/604cb32a73cb9db20715382b6d6b9be8.webm?t=1769452305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265020/extras/604cb32a73cb9db20715382b6d6b9be8.mp4?t=1769452305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The gameplay will change multiple times during the game experience, because the backpack itself can change its own nature.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >REACH THE EXTRACTION POINT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265020/extras/f33dea0cfcfc2ec3ce55a193c2b94260.poster.avif?t=1769452305\" width=426 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265020/extras/f33dea0cfcfc2ec3ce55a193c2b94260.webm?t=1769452305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265020/extras/f33dea0cfcfc2ec3ce55a193c2b94260.mp4?t=1769452305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level have its own extraction point, reach it before time runs out and try to solve the mystery!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE COMIC BOOK</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265020/extras/6fdc9463882b77b2088d8325fd5ebb09.poster.avif?t=1769452305\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265020/extras/6fdc9463882b77b2088d8325fd5ebb09.webm?t=1769452305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265020/extras/6fdc9463882b77b2088d8325fd5ebb09.mp4?t=1769452305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as a mysterious moustachioed man trapped in the backpack, but what about the backpack?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The parellel story of the backpack is narrated in the comic book, some special pages are interactable and can unlock some special features.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
